    <title>24小时直播间</title>
    <url>/2023/02/28/24%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E9%97%B4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="配置环境"><a href="#配置环境" class="headerlink" title="配置环境"></a>配置环境</h3><ol>
<li>centos7.9</li>
<li>服务器配置ffmpeg</li>
<li>安装screen： <code>yum -y install screen</code></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="创建进程"><a href="#创建进程" class="headerlink" title="创建进程"></a>创建进程</h3><ol>
<li>新建窗口：<code>screen -S Garrick</code></li>
<li>运行bash: <code>bash bash.sh</code><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">while true</span><br><span class="line">do</span><br><span class="line">    cd /usr/ffmpeg/video</span><br><span class="line">    # 定义推流地址和推流码</span><br><span class="line">    read -p &quot;输入你的推流地址和推流码(rtmp协议):&quot; rtmp</span><br><span class="line">    video=$(find ./ -type f | shuf -n 1)</span><br><span class="line">    ffmpeg -re -i &quot;$video&quot; -preset ultrafast -vcodec libx264 -g 60 -b:v 800k -c:a aac -b:a 92k -strict -2 -f flv $&#123;rtmp&#125;</span><br><span class="line">done</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>挂起进程<ol>
<li>查看当前screen进程列表：<code>screen -ls</code></li>
<li>更改状态为detached: <code>screen -d 进程名称</code></li>
<li>关闭某个进程： <code>screen -S 进程名称 -X quit</code></li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV14G4y1C7rq/?spm_id_from=333.880.my_history.page.click&vd_source=b3aa4a236cae89ccf31750ffb9a2fba7">视频教程</a></p>
]]></content>
